{"type": "article", "id": 22190, "title": "1500 支玫瑰花创意广告", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-14T08:23:44Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 116, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702164704eV3fXCKg8Wz29NRs.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">2014年情人节凌晨，法国创意机构 Kingsday 在巴黎市内安放了 1500 支玫瑰花。每一支玫瑰都放在了一个像火警器一样的红箱子里，上面写了一行文字“in case of love at first sight,break class（如果一见钟情，请敲碎玻璃）”。这些箱子是由一群跑酷高手在一晚上安放好的，它使用的玻璃材料也非常容易击碎，鼓励人们在遇见心爱的人时打开玻璃送出玫瑰。这个过程被拍成广告成为 Adweek 当年评选出的最佳户外广告之一，既聪明又浪漫。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164702l9qgbA3LxMXWR7oB.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.33265306\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164702OpaB5ef2PLXrZHku.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61944444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164703x57MJos9UwCiPYRu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.49259259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164703M6RS95eKY1C4ADsP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}